==Translingual==

===Etymology===
吠 is from 口 and 犬 which means to mouth and dog.
so the compose of these two words mean "bark"

Ancient Chinese said dog always bark while see something strange.
and so on we use 蜀犬吠日(means dog bark at the sun)
this refer to someone who is too exciting in common things

